00:48:42,085 --> 00:48:43,386
Lily?

483
00:49:03,874 --> 00:49:05,041
Where's Lily?

484
00:49:05,108 --> 00:49:06,542
Oh, God, honey, you scared me.

485
00:49:06,610 --> 00:49:08,077
Where is she?!

486
00:49:09,746 --> 00:49:11,414
Claire!

487
00:49:13,383 --> 00:49:14,583
Where is she?

488
00:49:14,651 --> 00:49:16,919
Come on, honey.
Claire, it is too late.

489
00:49:16,987 --> 00:49:18,587
Put it... Claire!

490
00:49:20,490 --> 00:49:21,791
- Claire!
- Where's Lily?

491
00:49:21,858 --> 00:49:23,793
- Stop it!
- How could you do that to her?

492
00:49:23,860 --> 00:49:26,662
She was my friend!
My only friend!

493
00:49:26,730 --> 00:49:28,864
Stop it!

494
00:49:28,932 --> 00:49:32,268
She did not belong to you!
She belonged to someone else.

495
00:49:32,336 --> 00:49:36,205
- Ow.
- What? What?

496
00:49:36,273 --> 00:49:38,107
Oh, my God.

497
00:49:38,175 --> 00:49:41,444
Oh, my God. Claire, honey,
where is this from?

498
00:49:41,511 --> 00:49:42,912
Who did this to you?

499
00:49:42,980 --> 00:49:44,246
I don't know!

500
00:49:45,415 --> 00:49:46,949
Claire!

501
00:51:43,800 --> 00:51:44,800
No!

502
00:52:39,422 --> 00:52:41,223
- Good morning.
- Hi.

503
00:52:46,363 --> 00:52:47,930
Are they real?

504
00:52:47,998 --> 00:52:50,432
You come on in,
I'll tell you all about them.

505
00:52:52,602 --> 00:52:54,336
See you in a bit.

506
00:52:54,404 --> 00:52:56,539
How many of you have
ever heard the expression

507
00:52:56,606 --> 00:52:58,307
"giving someone
the evil eye?"

508
00:52:58,375 --> 00:53:01,310
One of the best known and
perhaps the most frightening

509
00:53:01,378 --> 00:53:04,079
Latin American superstitions
is called Mal de Ojo.

510
00:53:04,147 --> 00:53:06,415
Ophelia?

511
00:53:06,483 --> 00:53:09,552
The belief is that the evil
spirit can direct bad luck

512
00:53:09,619 --> 00:53:13,422
or even injury at someone with
nothing more than a simple look.

